data.title: Mulligan’s Stew (4★)
data.meta_description: Find the best cocktails you can make with ingredients in your pantry.
data.text:
Mulligan’s Stew

Layer in a pousse café glass. Ignite the rum and allow it to burn for about 10 seconds. Extinguish the flame and toss back the drink. WARNING: the rim of the glass will be hot.
